16enum class ValueRepresentation : uint8_t;
17class MaglevCompilationInfo;
18class MaglevGraphLabeller;
19class Node;
20
21// Per-unit data, i.e. once per top-level function and once per inlined
22// function.
23class MaglevCompilationUnit : public ZoneObject {
24 public:
25 static MaglevCompilationUnit* New(Zone* zone, MaglevCompilationInfo* info,
26 Handle<JSFunction> function) {
27 return zone->New<MaglevCompilationUnit>(info, function);
28 }
29 static MaglevCompilationUnit* NewInner(
30 Zone* zone, const MaglevCompilationUnit* caller,
31 compiler::SharedFunctionInfoRef shared_function_info,
32 compiler::FeedbackVectorRef feedback_vector) {
33 return zone->New<MaglevCompilationUnit>(
34 caller->info(), caller, shared_function_info, feedback_vector);
35 }
36 static MaglevCompilationUnit* NewDummy(Zone* zone,
37 const MaglevCompilationUnit* caller,
38 int register_count,
39 int parameter_count) {
40 return zone->New<MaglevCompilationUnit>(caller->info(), caller,
41 register_count, parameter_count);
42 }
43
44 MaglevCompilationUnit(MaglevCompilationInfo* info,
45 Handle<JSFunction> function);
46
47 MaglevCompilationUnit(MaglevCompilationInfo* info,
48 const MaglevCompilationUnit* caller,
49 compiler::SharedFunctionInfoRef shared_function_info,
50 compiler::FeedbackVectorRef feedback_vector);
51
52 MaglevCompilationUnit(MaglevCompilationInfo* info,
53 const MaglevCompilationUnit* caller, int register_count,
54 int parameter_count);
55
56 MaglevCompilationInfo* info() const { return info_; }
57 const MaglevCompilationUnit* caller() const { return caller_; }
58 compiler::JSHeapBroker* broker() const;
59 LocalIsolate* local_isolate() const;
60 Zone* zone() const;
61 int register_count() const { return register_count_; }
62 int parameter_count() const { return parameter_count_; }
63 bool is_osr() const;
64 BytecodeOffset osr_offset() const;
65 int inlining_depth() const { return inlining_depth_; }
66 bool is_inline() const { return inlining_depth_ != 0; }
67 bool has_graph_labeller() const;
68 MaglevGraphLabeller* graph_labeller() const;
69 compiler::SharedFunctionInfoRef shared_function_info() const {
70 return shared_function_info_.value();
71 }
72 compiler::BytecodeArrayRef bytecode() const { return bytecode_.value(); }
73 compiler::FeedbackVectorRef feedback() const { return feedback_.value(); }
74
75 void RegisterNodeInGraphLabeller(const Node* node);
76
77 private:
78 MaglevCompilationInfo* const info_;
79 const MaglevCompilationUnit* const caller_;
80 const compiler::OptionalSharedFunctionInfoRef shared_function_info_;
81 const compiler::OptionalBytecodeArrayRef bytecode_;
82 const compiler::OptionalFeedbackVectorRef feedback_;
83 const int register_count_;
84 const int parameter_count_;
85 const int inlining_depth_;
86};

88} // namespace maglev
89} // namespace internal
